high_descs: Go forward to the bathtub.
Take the green cloth to the right out of the tub.
Turn right and take the cloth to the shelf in front of you, near the sink.
Put the cloth against the wall, on the right side of the shelf, below the right corner of the towel.
Go back to the tub.
Get the green cloth that is on the far left.
Turn right and return to the shelf near the sink.
Put the cloth at the center back of the shelf, to the left of the other green cloth.
anns.task_desc: Move two cloths from the tub to a bathroom shelf.

high_descs: Walk forward to the edge of the bathtub
Pick up the right most green cloth from the bathtub
Turn right and walk over to the small white cabinet by the door
Put the cloth down on top of the white cabinet
Turn left and walk back over to face the side of the bathtub
Pick up the left most green cloth from the tub
Turn right and walk back to the white cabinet
Put the green cloth down on the cabinet just left of the other cloth
anns.task_desc: Put the green cloths on the small white cabinet

high_descs: Move to stand at the right end of the bath tub closest to the sink.
Pick up the rightmost wash cloth from the tub.
Carry the wash cloth to stand facing the towel rack on the wall to the right of the sink.
Place the wash cloth on top of the white cabinet beneath the towel rack.
Move back to the tub.
Pick up the leftmost wash cloth, which is the one closest to the faucet.
Carry the wash cloth back to stand in front of the towel rack again.
Place the wash cloth on top of the white cabinet to the left of the one you previously put there.
anns.task_desc: Move two wash cloths from the tub to the top of the cabinet.
